#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn56.34"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.34:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.34:0.2"
msgid "4. Sīsapāvanavagga "
msgstr "4. In a Rosewood Forest "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.34:0.3"
msgid "34. Celasutta "
msgstr "34. Clothes "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn56.34:1.1"
msgid "“Āditte, bhikkhave, cele vā sīse vā kimassa karaṇīyan”ti? "
msgstr "“Mendicants, if your clothes or head were on fire, what would you do about it?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.34:1.2"
msgid "“Āditte, bhante, cele vā sīse vā, tasseva celassa vā sīsassa vā nibbāpanāya adhimatto chando ca vāyāmo ca ussāho ca ussoḷhī ca appaṭivānī ca sati ca sampajaññañca karaṇīyan”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, if our clothes or head were on fire, we’d apply intense enthusiasm, effort, zeal, vigor, perseverance, mindfulness, and situational awareness in order to extinguish it.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn56.34:2.1"
msgid "“Ādittaṃ, bhikkhave, celaṃ vā sīsaṃ vā ajjhupekkhitvā amanasikaritvā anabhisametānaṃ catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ yathābhūtaṃ abhisamayāya adhimatto chando ca vāyāmo ca ussāho ca ussoḷhī ca appaṭivānī ca sati ca sampajaññañca karaṇīyaṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, regarding your burning head or clothes with equanimity, not paying attention to them, you should apply intense enthusiasm, effort, zeal, vigor, perseverance, mindfulness, and situational awareness to truly comprehending the four noble truths. "

msgctxt "sn56.34:2.2"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn56.34:2.3"
msgid "Dukkhassa ariyasaccassa … pe … dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya ariyasaccassa. "
msgstr "The noble truths of suffering, its origin, its cessation, and the path. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn56.34:3.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.34:3.2"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

